summary: Woof your way onto Ethereum with Myro: Solana's playful pup lands on a new platform! - Remember Myro's mischievous romp on Solana? We made waves, paw-printed some impressive gains, and earned the love of a loyal pack. But Ethereum is where Myro truly throws off its leash and unleashes its full potential. Think boundless volume, and a community as diverse and exciting as a dog park at peak playtime.
